<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Affiliate Program - Ariatech</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/store.css" />
  <style>
    .page-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #232f3e 0%, #131921 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .page-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .content-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f08804 0%, #fa8900 100%);
      color: #131921;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .highlight-box h2 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .highlight-box .percentage {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      color: #232f3e;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .commission-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .commission-table th, .commission-table td {
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .commission-table th {
      background: #232f3e;
      color: white;
    }
    .commission-table tr:hover {
      background: #f8f8f8;
    }
    .cta-section {
      background: #232f3e;
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f08804;
      color: #131921;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #fa8900;
    }
    .benefits-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .benefits-list li {
      padding: 15px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    .check-icon {
      color: #28a745;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="theme-light">
  <header class="top-nav">
    <div class="nav-left">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Ariatech</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-center">
      <form class="search-bar" action="/" method="get">
        <select name="category" class="search-category">
          <option value="all">All</option>
          <option value="computer-parts">Computer Parts</option>
          <option value="computer">Computer</option>
          <option value="peripherals">Peripherals</option>
          <option value="storage">Storage</option>
        </select>
        <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Search Ariatech computers" class="search-input" />
        <button class="search-button" type="submit">Search</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="/admin" class="nav-link">Admin</a>
      <a href="#" class="nav-link">Cart</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <h1>Ariatech Affiliate Program</h1>
      <p>Partner with us and earn commissions by promoting quality computers and tech products.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <div class="percentage">Up to 10%</div>
        <h2>Commission on Every Sale</h2>
        <p>Earn generous commissions for every customer you refer who makes a purchase.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Why Join Our Affiliate Program?</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>High Commissions</h3>
          <p>Earn up to 10% commission on every sale. The more you sell, the more you earn.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Cookie Duration</h3>
          <p>Enjoy a 30-day cookie duration. You get credit for sales made within 30 days of the initial click.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Wide Product Range</h3>
          <p>Promote laptops, desktops, gaming rigs, parts, and accessories from top brands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Real-Time Tracking</h3>
          <p>Access your dashboard to track clicks, conversions, and earnings in real-time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Marketing Support</h3>
          <p>Get access to banners, links, and promotional materials to help you succeed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Fast Payouts</h3>
          <p>Receive your commissions monthly via PayPal or bank transfer. Minimum payout: $50.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Commission Structure</h2>
      <table class="commission-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Product Category</th>
            <th>Commission Rate</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Laptops & Notebooks</td>
            <td>8%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Desktop Computers</td>
            <td>8%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Gaming PCs & Rigs</td>
            <td>10%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Computer Parts</td>
            <td>6%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Peripherals</td>
            <td>5%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Accessories</td>
            <td>5%</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left: 25px;">
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Sign Up:</strong> Fill out our affiliate application form. We'll review and approve within 48 hours.</li>
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Get Your Links:</strong> Once approved, you'll receive unique affiliate links and marketing materials.</li>
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Promote:</strong> Share your links on your website, blog, social media, or email list.</li>
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Earn:</strong> Earn commissions on every qualifying sale made through your links.</li>
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Get Paid:</strong> Receive your earnings via PayPal or bank transfer on a monthly basis.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Who Can Join?</h2>
      <p>Our affiliate program is open to:</p>
      <ul class="benefits-list">
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Content creators and bloggers</li>
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Tech reviewers and YouTubers</li>
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Social media influencers</li>
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Website owners with tech-related content</li>
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Email marketers</li>
        <li><span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span> Tech enthusiast communities</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Join Today!</h2>
      <p>Start earning by promoting quality computers and tech products.</p>
      <a href="#" class="cta-button">Become an Affiliate</a>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <h3>How do I track my sales?</h3>
        <p>We provide a real-time affiliate dashboard where you can track clicks, conversions, and earnings.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <h3>When do I get paid?</h3>
        <p>Payments are processed on the 15th of each month for the previous month's earnings.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <h3>Is there a cost to join?</h3>
        <p>No, joining our affiliate program is completely free.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <h3>How long do cookies last?</h3>
        <p>Our affiliate cookies last for 30 days from the initial click.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <a href="#" class="back-to-top">Back to top</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-columns">
      <div>
        <h4>Get to know us</h4>
        <a href="/about">About Ariatech</a>
        <a href="#">Careers</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Make money with us</h4>
        <a href="/sell-computer">Sell computers</a>
        <a href="/affiliate-program">Affiliate program</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Let us help you</h4>
        <a href="#">Your account</a>
        <a href="#">Help</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ariatech Computers</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
